Fill coffeemaker with water. Mix ground cinnamon with coffee and brew one pot. While coffee is brewing, heat milk in microwave on low until warm. Pour equal amounts of coffee into 6 mugs. Add 1 teaspoon SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and 1/2 teaspoon cocoa to each mug. Mix well; top off with milk. Garnish with cinnamon sticks.